comment: yes! I completely agree with there not being any bad seasons because we have to accept them for how different each of them are yet they're all consistently talked about and entertaining and GOOD tbh

Awesome video, as usual!  You are a master at critical analysis. It is true that there is no "worst" season, but I never thought about it like that until you pointed it out. They are all conceptually sound and well executed; it's just a matter of preference. I can't wait for the new season. I was a teenager in the 80's, so I'm pretty stoked to see what they do with it.
